description.en: Bullers coin is a cryptocurrency powered by ethereun main network, an eco-system of tools designed for entrepreneurs in the rising future economies. Bullers Coin mission is to unlock the potential of the world’s largest growing workforce by creating, earning, spending and saving opportunities. Users are able to transition in and out of the ecosystem by converting fiat currency into cryptocurrency and vice versa.!
